  "texts": [
    "It is important to address cases where these conditions are not satisfied.",
    "Having the LLM ask follow-up questions is one possible solution.",
    "Another alternative is to have the LLM rephrase the question to match one from a reference list, which are mapped to human generated answers.",
    "The information presented to the user is guaranteed to be correct, although it may not be helpful if it answers the wrong question.",
    "To avoid this, the rephrased question can be presented to the user to validate that it is the correct intent."
  ],
